[[Image:CantoneseTofuwithShrimp.jpg|thumb|right|200px|Fried tofu with shrimp]]

===Banquet/night dishes===
There are a number of dishes that are often served in Cantonese restaurants exclusively during dinner. Traditionally [[dim sum]] restaurants stop serving [[bamboo]]-basket dishes after [[yum cha]] hour and begin offering an entirely different menu in the evening. Some dishes are more standard while others are quite regional. Some are customized for special purposes such as [[Chinese marriage]]s or [[banquet]]s. Salt and pepper dishes are one of the few spicy dishes.

