===Delicacies===
There are some dishes that are prized within the culture. These dishes range from being relatively affordable to very expensive. Most of these have been around in the [[Far East]] for a long time, while some are becoming available around the world. Many of these prized animals have serious and controversial [[animal rights]] issues, such as the finning of [[Shark cartilage]]s.

