* [http://www.archive.org/stream/Tischendorf.V.Various/01.CodexEphraemiSyriRescriptus.FragUtriusqTest.1845.#page/n9/mode/2up ''Codex Ephraemi Syri rescriptus, sive Fragmenta Veteris Testamenti''], Lipsiae 1845
